<div class="nb-section" id="interview">
<div class="section-header purple"><h2>💻 Pure Coding Interview Questions</h2></div>
<div class="question interview"><p><strong>Q1.</strong> What is the purpose of the <code>WHERE</code> clause and at which step does it execute in the SQL Order of Execution?</p></div>
<div class="code-cell" id="cell-7">
