</h3></div>
<div class="question"><p><strong>Q1.</strong> Write a query that shows each employee''s <code>first_name</code>, <code>last_name</code>, <code>salary</code>, and their <code>department_name</code>. Use INNER JOIN to link employees to departments.</p></div>
